TITLE: Episode 115 - The Water's Warm w/ Dr. Mav
DESCRIPTION: Look who's back! Maddie and Jessie resurface from the depths of their busy lives and (maternity!) brain fog to bring you a conversation with Dr. Irene Mavrikakis, a board certified interventional spine and musculoskeletal specialist. She has been outspoken in the fight for medical sovereignty and bodily autonomy.
